caption.paragraph: TABLE I. Estimates of Evolutionary Divergence between Sequences. The number of base differences per site from between sequences are shown. The rate variation among sites was modeled with a gamma distribution (shape parameter = 1). Codon positions included were 1st+2nd+3rd+Noncoding. All ambiguous positions were removed for each sequence pair (pairwise deletion option). There were a total of 657 positions in the final dataset. Evolutionary analyses were conducted in MEGA X.
